From: Steffen Sledz <sledz@dresearch-fe.de>
Date: Wed, 17 Jul 2013 11:49:22 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] systemd-halt.service: always poweroff on halt

halt without poweroff makes no sense on our hipos hardware.

Signed-off-by: Steffen Sledz <sledz@dresearch-fe.de>
---
 units/systemd-halt.service.in | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/units/systemd-halt.service.in b/units/systemd-halt.service.in
index d55d622..e4e3f8d 100644
--- a/units/systemd-halt.service.in
+++ b/units/systemd-halt.service.in
@@ -14,4 +14,4 @@ After=shutdown.target umount.target final.target
 
 [Service]
 Type=oneshot
-ExecStart=@SYSTEMCTL@ --force halt
+ExecStart=@SYSTEMCTL@ --force poweroff
